Class AbstractRedisAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lwerner.flink.percentiles.redis.AbstractRedisAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FakeRedisAdapter, JedisRedisAdapter

    public abstract class AbstractRedisAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class AbstractRedisAdapter Holds the abstract methods for working with redis in this application and provides a factory method.

    Lukas Werner
